{
  "page": "Roger of Pennytree",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">\"Roger\" redirects here. For other characters with the same name, see <a href=\"/index.php/Roger_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Roger (disambiguation)\">Roger (disambiguation)</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Roger of Pennytree</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Roger_of_Pennytree_TMK_comic.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Roger of Pennytree TMK comic.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fa/Roger_of_Pennytree_TMK_comic.png/350px-Roger_of_Pennytree_TMK_comic.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"282\" srcset=\"/images/f/fa/Roger_of_Pennytree_TMK_comic.png 1.5x\" /></a><div>Roger of Pennytree, by Mike S. Miller</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n~<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_177_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">177</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/184_AC\" title=\"184 AC\">184&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Pennytree\" title=\"Pennytree\">Pennytree</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafroger_of_pennytree.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafroger_of_pennytree.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/196_AC\" title=\"196 AC\">196&#160;AC</a><br />the <a href=\"/index.php/Redgrass_Field\" title=\"Redgrass Field\">Redgrass Field</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sworn_Sword\" title=\"The Sworn Sword\">The Sworn Sword</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Mystery_Knight\" title=\"The Mystery Knight\">The Mystery Knight</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Roger of Pennytree</b> was the squire and nephew of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Arlan_of_Pennytree\" title=\"Arlan of Pennytree\">Arlan of Pennytree</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Roger_of_Pennytree&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Roger died at the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Redgrass_Field\" title=\"Battle of the Redgrass Field\">Battle of the Redgrass Field</a> after Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gormon_Peake\" title=\"Gormon Peake\">Gormon Peake</a> smashed his head with a mace.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtss.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a> served as Arlan's squire after the war until the old <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a>'s death. As Duncan played a role in <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Blackfyre_Rebellion\" title=\"Second Blackfyre Rebellion\">events</a> that led to Gormon's execution, he felt he had avenged Roger's death.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Roger_of_Pennytree&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Grandfather</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"></tr>\n<tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"fon